dcterms:creator: W. Li
L. Wang
E. Agustsson
L. Van Gool
dcterms:description: WebVision-1000 contains 2.4M noisy-labeled training images crawled from Flickr and Google, with keywords from 1000 class-labels in ILSVRC-2012. The estimated web label accuracy is 48%.
dcterms:title: WebVision-1000

dcterms:creator: L. Bossard
M. Guillaumin
L. Van Gool
dcterms:description: Food-101N is a web dataset with 310k images classified into 101 food categories. Images are crawled from Google, Yelp, etc. It includes 60k human verification labels indicating the correctness of web labels.
dcterms:title: Food-101N

dcterms:description: WebVision-500 is a quarter-sized version of WebVision-1000 for evaluation and ablation study in low cost without losing generalization. It randomly samples one-half categories with one-half samples in the training set.
dcterms:title: WebVision-500
